# Business Development Intern — LinkedIn Job Post

🚀 **We're Hiring: Business Development Intern — Blackmont Consulting**

Blackmont Consulting is looking for a driven, self-motivated **Business Development Intern** to join our team. This is a hands-on, performance-driven role — perfect for someone who wants real ownership from day one and is ready to build practical business development skills that translate directly into a career.

## What You'll Be Doing
- Researching companies that could benefit from Blackmont's services
- Reaching out to potential clients via email and following up professionally
- Supporting proposal preparation and the client journey from first contact through to project completion
- Tracking your outreach activity, attending weekly team meetings, and working towards closing at least one project during your internship

## Who We're Looking For
- Self-driven and proactive
- A strong, confident communicator
- Detail-oriented with good follow-through
- Comfortable working independently
- Resilient — cold outreach means handling unanswered messages and declined opportunities as part of the job

## What You'll Gain
Real-world business development experience, practical commercial skills, and a growing professional network — all while contributing meaningfully to live client work.

📄 Full role details are in the Business Development Role Overview — candidates will be asked to complete screening questions as part of the application process.

